S.FORM: Brent Barry kakilimaan u tatama, u miunduay, u Amilika a tademaw. nilacul ci Brent Barry, nalecuh ciniza i Hempstead, New York, nanu syubay kanas mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput, pahanhanan tu kawaw ayza.
